    "push": "On hit, push target 10ft away (target can make STR save to resist).",
    "sap": "On hit, target has disadvantage on its next attack roll.",
    "slow": "On hit, reduce target's speed by 10ft until start of your next turn.",
    "topple": "On hit, target must make STR save or fall prone.",
